[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"02977\" class=\"\">Josiah</st> was <st data-num=\"08083\" class=\"\">eight</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">old</st> when he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">became king</st>, and he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">reigned</st> for <st data-num=\"07970\" class=\"\">thirty</st>-<st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> His <st data-num=\"08034 0517\">mother</st><n id=\"2\" /> was <st data-num=\"03040\" class=\"\">Jedidah</st>, <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughter</st> of <st data-num=\"05718\" class=\"\">Adaiah</st>, from <st data-num=\"01218\" class=\"\">Bozkath</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"03477\" class=\"\">what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">approved</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">followed</st> in his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestor</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03605 01870\">footsteps</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> he did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">deviate</st> to the <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right</st> or the <st data-num=\"08040\" class=\"\">left</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">In the <st data-num=\"01961 08083 06240\">eighteenth</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">year</st> of <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"02977\" class=\"\">Josiah\u2019s</st> reign, the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st> <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"0683\" class=\"\">Azaliah</st>, <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"04918\" class=\"\">Meshullam</st>, to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> with <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">these orders</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">Go up</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st> the <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">high</st> <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> and have him <st data-num=\"05413\" class=\"\">melt down</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st> that has been <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">by</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">and</st> has been <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">collected</st> by the <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">guards</st> at the <st data-num=\"05592\" class=\"\">door</st>. ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "Have them <st data-num=\"05414 05921 03027\">hand</st> it <st data-num=\"05414 05921 03027\">over</st> to the <st data-num=\"04399\" class=\"\">construction</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">foremen</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">assigned</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>. They in turn should <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">pay</st> the <st data-num=\"0834 01004\">temple</st> <st data-num=\"06213 04399\">workers</st> to <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">repair</st> <st data-num=\"0919 01004\">it</st>,<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "including <st data-num=\"02796\" class=\"\">craftsmen</st>, <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">builders</st>, and <st data-num=\"01443\" class=\"\">masons</st>, and should <st data-num=\"07069\" class=\"\">buy</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">wood</st> and <st data-num=\"04274\" class=\"\">chiseled</st> <st data-num=\"068\" class=\"\">stone</st> for the <st data-num=\"02388 01004\">repair work</st>.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "Do <st data-num=\"0389 03808\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02803 0854\">audit</st> the foremen who disburse the <st data-num=\"03701 05414 05921 03027\">silver</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">they</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">are</st> <st data-num=\"0530\" class=\"\">honest</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st> the <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">high</st> <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> <st data-num=\"0559 05921\">informed</st> <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st>, \u201cI <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">found</st> the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st> of the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>.\u201d <st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">gave</st> the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st> and he <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">read</st> it.",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"07725 04428 01697 0559\">reported</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cYour <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st> <st data-num=\"05413\" class=\"\">melted down</st> the <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st> in the <st data-num=\"04672 01004\">temple</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">handed</st> it <st data-num=\"05921 03027\">over</st> to the <st data-num=\"04399\" class=\"\">construction</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">foremen</st> <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">assigned</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st> <st data-num=\"05046 0559\">told</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> has <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st> me a <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st>.\u201d <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">read</st> it <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">out loud</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>. ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">When</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> of the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st>, he <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">tore</st> his <st data-num=\"0899\" class=\"\">clothes</st>. ",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">ordered</st> <st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st>, <st data-num=\"0296\" class=\"\">Ahikam</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st>, <st data-num=\"05907\" class=\"\">Achbor</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"04320\" class=\"\">Micaiah</st>, <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st>, and <st data-num=\"06222\" class=\"\">Asaiah</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>, ",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st>, <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek an oracle from</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01157\" class=\"\">for</st> me <st data-num=\"01157\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"01157\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>. Find out <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">about</st> the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> of <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st> that has been <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">discovered</st>. <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"02534 0834 01931\">fury</st> has been <st data-num=\"03341\" class=\"\">ignited</st> against us, <st data-num=\"05921 0834\">because</st> our <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st> have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085 05921\">obeyed</st> the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> of <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st> by <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">doing</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> that it <st data-num=\"03789 05921\">instructs</st> us to do.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st>, <st data-num=\"0296\" class=\"\">Ahikam</st>, <st data-num=\"05907\" class=\"\">Achbor</st>, <st data-num=\"08227\" class=\"\">Shaphan</st>, and <st data-num=\"06222\" class=\"\">Asaiah</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"02468\" class=\"\">Huldah</st> the <st data-num=\"05031\" class=\"\">prophetess</st>, the <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> of <st data-num=\"07967\" class=\"\">Shullam</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"08616\" class=\"\">Tikvah</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02745\" class=\"\">Harhas</st>, the <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">supervisor</st> of the <st data-num=\"0899\" class=\"\">wardrobe</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> (<st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">She</st> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">lived in</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st> in the <st data-num=\"04932\" class=\"\">Mishneh</st><n id=\"2\" /> district.) They <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">stated</st> their <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">business</st>,<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "and she <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> them: \u201c<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>: \u2018<st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">Say</st> this to the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> you <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me: ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>: \u2018I <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">am about</st> to <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">place</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">and</st> its <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">residents</st>, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">things</st> in the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> has <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">read</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "This will happen <st data-num=\"08478 0834\">because</st> they have <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandoned</st> me and <st data-num=\"06999\" class=\"\">offered sacrifices</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"0312\" class=\"\">other</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st>, <st data-num=\"04616 03707\">angering</st> me with <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">idols</st> they have <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">made</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> My <st data-num=\"02534\" class=\"\">anger</st> will <st data-num=\"03341\" class=\"\">ignite</st> against <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">place</st> and will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be <st data-num=\"03518\" class=\"\">extinguished</st>!\u2019\u201d ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0559 0413\">Say</st> <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, who <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> you to <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek an oracle from</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>: \u201c<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> concerning the <st data-num=\"01697 0834\">words</st> you have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st>: ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "\u2018You displayed a <st data-num=\"03282 07401\">sensitive</st> <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">spirit</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"03665\" class=\"\">humbled</st> yourself <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> when you <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">how</st> I <st data-num=\"01696 05921\">intended</st> to <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">place</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">and</st> its <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">residents</st> into an <st data-num=\"08047\" class=\"\">appalling example</st> of an <st data-num=\"07045\" class=\"\">accursed</st> people.<n id=\"2\" /> You <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">tore</st> your <st data-num=\"0899\" class=\"\">clothes</st> and <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">wept</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> me, <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> you,\u2019 <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. ",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Kings",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "\u2018<st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Therefore</st> <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">allow</st> you <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">die</st> and be <st data-num=\"0622 0413 06913\">buried</st> in <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">You</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> have to <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">witness</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"07451 0834\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">place</st>.\u2019\u201d\u2019\u201d Then they <st data-num=\"07725 01697\">reported back to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  }
]